4.2 Solution of State Equations

The system can be solved numerically. For small time steps Δt:

T(t+\Delta t) = T(t) + \frac{\Delta t}{C_{th}} \left[ P_c(t) + \alpha A_s \Phi(t) - \epsilon \sigma A_r (T^4 - T_{env}^4) - \frac{\Delta Q_{pcm}}{\Delta t} \right]

For linearized analysis around operating point T_0:

T^4 \approx T_0^4 + 4T_0^3 (T - T_0)

Thus:

